        <h3 class="text-center text-slate-600 font-medium text-xl">Property Details</h3>
        <p class="text-center mx-auto px-8 max-w-md text-slate-600">
          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Natus, dolore? Perspiciatis libero rem iste alias qui voluptas ex quaerat magnam!
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="w-[100%] h-[49%] sm:h-full sm:w-[28%] lg:w-[38%] xl:w-[49%] ml-0 mt-auto sm:mt-0 sm:ml-auto bg-slate-200 hover:bg-slate-100 transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col justify-center items-center gap-7 rounded-xl shadow-xl">
